name: WATERFLOW Collaboration
description: This is an open invitation for any artist that buys this nft is also asked to be an entrant to a fun little side project and to use it as your base too.. You can change size or use only a pxl all is ok, Put your touch on top.. And go nuts just post your work with the tag #WATERFLOW & #COart Look forward to seeing and buying some cool designs.. And price should be between .1 - .5 , again tho its all up to you what your starting price or amount will be ....
